---
---
<section class="relative min-h-screen w-full pt-32 pb-20 overflow-hidden bg-[#FDFCFB]">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8 flex flex-col items-center">
    <div class="text-center reveal mb-16">
      <span class="mb-6 inline-block text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.6em] text-[#C5A059]">
        Ciência, Ética & Arte
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-6xl font-medium leading-[1.1] text-[#1A1A1A] sm:text-8xl tracking-tighter">
        Realçando Sua <br />
        <span class="italic font-light">Beleza Natural</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-10 mx-auto max-w-xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-[#1A1A1A]/50 font-light">
        Um novo conceito em harmonização e rejuvenescimento, onde a técnica avançada da biomedicina encontra o olhar artístico individualizado.
      </p>
      
      <div class="mt-12 flex flex-col items-center gap-8">
        <a href="#contato" class="btn-elegant">
          Agendar Consulta
        </a>
        <a href="#tratamentos" class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-[#1A1A1A]/40 hover:text-[#C5A059] transition-colors">
          Explorar Procedimentos ↓
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal relative w-full max-w-5xl aspect-[16/9] overflow-hidden rounded-[40px] shadow-2xl shadow-[#C5A059]/10">
      <img 
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1594824476967-48c8b964273f?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1600" 
        alt="Dra. Carolina Mendes em seu consultório" 
        class="h-full w-full object-cover"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/20 to-transparent"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
